{
  "stem": "25639.7",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Many, many years later, I found that my father and my brother Shandor were working only about 60 miles from Beendorf, where I was, in the mother factory, where they dynamited silos and tunnels for the V1 and V2 rockets.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Now, that is where the action was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "That is where they tested these rockets.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And neither of us knew that the other was alive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this happened only a few years ago when one day I decided to plot on a map the concentration camps that I was in, and that my father and my brother Shandor were in.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Dora-Mittlebau.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Dora-Mittlebau.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "D-O-R-A dash M-I-T-T-L-E-B-A-U.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I'd like to move on to the next camp, because after Beendorf I was sent to Ravensbruck, which was strictly a women's camp.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was notorious for its vicious medical experiments.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But, thank God, I was not subjected to any of these cruel experiments.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a whole area that was affected by this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But there in-- in-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Ravensbruck, there were many, many non-Jewish political prisoners, people who worked in the underground, Danes, French, British.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were caught.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And for example, I have a friend in Marin County, who was-- who is a non-Jewish woman and was born in England, married a Frenchmen and lived in Paris.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "During the war, she worked for the underground.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She had a little son about six or seven years old.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she was caught and was sent to Ravensbruck.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there are many, many people like this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I understand that Himmler himself had a sister-- and this is apparently a very little-known story, but I learned this in Germany, actually, that he had a-- has a sister-- or had a sister, definitely had.",
      "word_count": 37
    }
  ],
